<subSubSection id="C31265792156FFFBFF221A06FB20FDFD" pageId="4" pageNumber="215" type="diagnosis">
<paragraph id="8BB736F22156FFFBFF221A06FB20FDFD" blockId="4.[151,1437,259,538]" pageId="4" pageNumber="215">
<emphasis id="B97CEAE02156FFFBFF221A06FE8FFEF9" bold="true" box="[151,273,259,285]" pageId="4" pageNumber="215">
<emphasis id="B97CEAE02156FFFBFF221A06FE94FEF9" bold="true" box="[151,266,259,285]" italics="true" pageId="4" pageNumber="215">Diagnosis</emphasis>
.
</emphasis>
Length 
<quantity id="4CF09B172156FFFBFEC41A06FE5AFEFA" box="[369,452,259,286]" metricMagnitude="-2" metricUnit="m" metricValue="1.7" pageId="4" pageNumber="215" unit="mm" value="17.0">17 mm</quantity>
. Width 
<quantity id="4CF09B172156FFFBFDA81A06FDEEFEFA" box="[541,624,259,286]" metricMagnitude="-2" metricUnit="m" metricValue="1.6" pageId="4" pageNumber="215" unit="mm" value="16.0">16 mm</quantity>
. Humeral angles projection strongly developed, spiniform (
<figureCitation id="13332A772156FFFBFAA61A06FA0EFEF9" box="[1299,1424,259,285]" captionStart="FIGURE 1" captionStartId="3.[151,250,1866,1890]" captionTargetBox="[171,1412,191,1824]" captionTargetId="figure-20@3.[171,1416,181,1841]" captionTargetPageId="3" captionText="FIGURE 1. Grammedessa. A–B: G. hamata comb.n. A: Dorsal view. B: Ventral view. C–D: G. nigricava sp.n. C: Dorsal view. D: Ventral view. E–F: G. longispina sp.n. E: Dorsal view. F: Ventral view. G–H: G. fundicava sp.n. G: Dorsal view. H: Ventral view. I–J: G. graciligramma sp.n. I: Dorsal view. J: Ventral view. K–L: G. stichtocephala sp.n. K: Dorsal view. L: Ventral view. M–N: G. acalyptoprocta sp.n. M: Dorsal view. N: Ventral view. Scale = 10 mm." figureDoi="http://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.6500667" httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/6500667/files/figure.png" pageId="4" pageNumber="215">Fig. 1A–B</figureCitation>
). Dorsal surface green, punctures on brown spots forming irregular lines (
<figureCitation id="13332A772156FFFBFC091A22FB8AFEA5" box="[956,1044,295,321]" captionStart="FIGURE 1" captionStartId="3.[151,250,1866,1890]" captionTargetBox="[171,1412,191,1824]" captionTargetId="figure-20@3.[171,1416,181,1841]" captionTargetPageId="3" captionText="FIGURE 1. Grammedessa. A–B: G. hamata comb.n. A: Dorsal view. B: Ventral view. C–D: G. nigricava sp.n. C: Dorsal view. D: Ventral view. E–F: G. longispina sp.n. E: Dorsal view. F: Ventral view. G–H: G. fundicava sp.n. G: Dorsal view. H: Ventral view. I–J: G. graciligramma sp.n. I: Dorsal view. J: Ventral view. K–L: G. stichtocephala sp.n. K: Dorsal view. L: Ventral view. M–N: G. acalyptoprocta sp.n. M: Dorsal view. N: Ventral view. Scale = 10 mm." figureDoi="http://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.6500667" httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/6500667/files/figure.png" pageId="4" pageNumber="215">Fig. 1A</figureCitation>
). Costal margin and disc of corium homogeneously punctured; hypocostal ridge with punctures and spots dark brown to black. Beneath with three yellow stripes separating two green areas densely spotted, containing punctures on the thorax (
<figureCitation id="13332A772156FFFBFB771A6AFA87FE6D" box="[1218,1305,367,393]" captionStart="FIGURE 1" captionStartId="3.[151,250,1866,1890]" captionTargetBox="[171,1412,191,1824]" captionTargetId="figure-20@3.[171,1416,181,1841]" captionTargetPageId="3" captionText="FIGURE 1. Grammedessa. A–B: G. hamata comb.n. A: Dorsal view. B: Ventral view. C–D: G. nigricava sp.n. C: Dorsal view. D: Ventral view. E–F: G. longispina sp.n. E: Dorsal view. F: Ventral view. G–H: G. fundicava sp.n. G: Dorsal view. H: Ventral view. I–J: G. graciligramma sp.n. I: Dorsal view. J: Ventral view. K–L: G. stichtocephala sp.n. K: Dorsal view. L: Ventral view. M–N: G. acalyptoprocta sp.n. M: Dorsal view. N: Ventral view. Scale = 10 mm." figureDoi="http://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.6500667" httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/6500667/files/figure.png" pageId="4" pageNumber="215">Fig. 1B</figureCitation>
). Propleura mostly green; densely punctured, punctures on dark brown spots. Antennae brown, first three segments finely spotted. Legs greenish-brown. Metasternal process yellow with few lateral spots (
<figureCitation id="13332A772156FFFBFBFF1AB2FB3DFE35" box="[1098,1187,439,465]" captionStart="FIGURE 1" captionStartId="3.[151,250,1866,1890]" captionTargetBox="[171,1412,191,1824]" captionTargetId="figure-20@3.[171,1416,181,1841]" captionTargetPageId="3" captionText="FIGURE 1. Grammedessa. A–B: G. hamata comb.n. A: Dorsal view. B: Ventral view. C–D: G. nigricava sp.n. C: Dorsal view. D: Ventral view. E–F: G. longispina sp.n. E: Dorsal view. F: Ventral view. G–H: G. fundicava sp.n. G: Dorsal view. H: Ventral view. I–J: G. graciligramma sp.n. I: Dorsal view. J: Ventral view. K–L: G. stichtocephala sp.n. K: Dorsal view. L: Ventral view. M–N: G. acalyptoprocta sp.n. M: Dorsal view. N: Ventral view. Scale = 10 mm." figureDoi="http://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.6500667" httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/6500667/files/figure.png" pageId="4" pageNumber="215">Fig. 1B</figureCitation>
). Connexivum green. Rounded area lateral to evaporatorium dark green (
<figureCitation id="13332A772156FFFBFD541ADEFCA4FE11" box="[737,826,475,501]" captionStart="FIGURE 1" captionStartId="3.[151,250,1866,1890]" captionTargetBox="[171,1412,191,1824]" captionTargetId="figure-20@3.[171,1416,181,1841]" captionTargetPageId="3" captionText="FIGURE 1. Grammedessa. A–B: G. hamata comb.n. A: Dorsal view. B: Ventral view. C–D: G. nigricava sp.n. C: Dorsal view. D: Ventral view. E–F: G. longispina sp.n. E: Dorsal view. F: Ventral view. G–H: G. fundicava sp.n. G: Dorsal view. H: Ventral view. I–J: G. graciligramma sp.n. I: Dorsal view. J: Ventral view. K–L: G. stichtocephala sp.n. K: Dorsal view. L: Ventral view. M–N: G. acalyptoprocta sp.n. M: Dorsal view. N: Ventral view. Scale = 10 mm." figureDoi="http://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.6500667" httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/6500667/files/figure.png" pageId="4" pageNumber="215">Fig. 1B</figureCitation>
). Yellow lateral stripe with black rounded spots (
<figureCitation id="13332A772156FFFBFADA1ADEFF27FDFD" captionStart="FIGURE 1" captionStartId="3.[151,250,1866,1890]" captionTargetBox="[171,1412,191,1824]" captionTargetId="figure-20@3.[171,1416,181,1841]" captionTargetPageId="3" captionText="FIGURE 1. Grammedessa. A–B: G. hamata comb.n. A: Dorsal view. B: Ventral view. C–D: G. nigricava sp.n. C: Dorsal view. D: Ventral view. E–F: G. longispina sp.n. E: Dorsal view. F: Ventral view. G–H: G. fundicava sp.n. G: Dorsal view. H: Ventral view. I–J: G. graciligramma sp.n. I: Dorsal view. J: Ventral view. K–L: G. stichtocephala sp.n. K: Dorsal view. L: Ventral view. M–N: G. acalyptoprocta sp.n. M: Dorsal view. N: Ventral view. Scale = 10 mm." figureDoi="http://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.6500667" httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/6500667/files/figure.png" pageId="4" pageNumber="215">Fig. 1B</figureCitation>
). Parameres long, Y-shaped (
<figureCitation id="13332A772156FFFBFDB41AFAFDC4FDFD" box="[513,602,511,537]" captionStart="FIGURE 2" captionStartId="4.[151,250,1811,1835]" captionTargetBox="[153,1418,576,1785]" captionTargetId="figure-159@4.[153,1434,561,1788]" captionTargetPageId="4" captionText="FIGURE 2. Genitalia of G. hamata comb.n. A–C: Male genitalia. A: Pygophore in dorsal view. B: Pygophore in ventral view. C: Pygophore in posterior view. D: Female genital plates in ventral view. Dr: Dorsal rim. Vf8: Valvifers 8. Vf9: Valvifer 9. Gc: Genital cup. Lt8: Laterotergites 8. Lt9: Laterotergites 9. Prc: Proctiger. Pla: Posterolateral angles. Pr: Parameres. Pyg: Pygophore. Vr: Ventral Rim. X: Segment X. Scale = 1 mm." figureDoi="http://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.6500673" httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/6500673/files/figure.png" pageId="4" pageNumber="215">Fig. 2C</figureCitation>
). Proctiger keel along the entire median line (
<figureCitation id="13332A772156FFFBFBEC1AFAFB2FFDFD" box="[1113,1201,511,537]" captionStart="FIGURE 2" captionStartId="4.[151,250,1811,1835]" captionTargetBox="[153,1418,576,1785]" captionTargetId="figure-159@4.[153,1434,561,1788]" captionTargetPageId="4" captionText="FIGURE 2. Genitalia of G. hamata comb.n. A–C: Male genitalia. A: Pygophore in dorsal view. B: Pygophore in ventral view. C: Pygophore in posterior view. D: Female genital plates in ventral view. Dr: Dorsal rim. Vf8: Valvifers 8. Vf9: Valvifer 9. Gc: Genital cup. Lt8: Laterotergites 8. Lt9: Laterotergites 9. Prc: Proctiger. Pla: Posterolateral angles. Pr: Parameres. Pyg: Pygophore. Vr: Ventral Rim. X: Segment X. Scale = 1 mm." figureDoi="http://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.6500673" httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/6500673/files/figure.png" pageId="4" pageNumber="215">Fig. 2C</figureCitation>
).
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
